  "instructions": [
    "Combine ripe tomatoes, Massaman paste, garlic, and shallots in a blender and blend until smooth.",
    "Strain the mixture through a fine-mesh sieve into a bowl.",
    "In a separate pan, heat olive oil over medium heat and add fermented kimchi, red pepper flakes, and a pinch of salt.",
    "Cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally, until the kimchi is caramelized and slightly crispy.",
    "Stir in the kimchi mixture into the tomato mixture and combine well.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning as needed.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a serving bowl and top with chopped fresh cilantro and crunchy fried shallots.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
